definition.text: Results are organized in several categories, and each category is represented by a tab grouping results matching the category...

paragraphs.text: I'll explain each briefly and set you free to look around:
All: features results from all categories.
Nodes: Node Type matches containing the phrase.
Concepts: includes notions such as References.
Topics: large themes covered in sequenced pages.
Tutorials: features the pages that make up tutorials.
Reviews: features users reviews on plugins , etc...
Books: collections of topics organized in chapters that cover entire app domains, for an orderly read.
Workspace: returns nodes that are present in the active workspace... click to go to them!
